title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Eliminators
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Eliminators
description:
In this episode of Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and Joe dive head first into the 1986 cyborg time-travel adventure film “Eliminators,” which has robots, cavemen, kung-fu and more boat-related combat than you’re probably ready for.
